 almost\nperfect representation of the lattice, with the exception of cases where\nmicro-bifurcation occurs, which is shown to leave the equivalent solid\nunaffected. Therefore, the presented results pave the way for the design of\narchitected cellular materials to be used in applications where extreme\ndeformations are involved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 16:16:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 12:35:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-22"}
