e of\nindependent observations, breaking degeneracies that exist in simpler models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 17:24:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Apr 2020 21:30:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 16:18:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-17"}
