nautocorrelation inequalities of the form \\begin{equation*}\n  \\min_{ \\mathbf{t} \\in [0,1]^d } \\int_{\\mathbf{R}} \\prod_{i=1}^n\\ f(x+\n\\mathbf{t} \\cdot a_i)\\ \\mathrm{d}x\\ \\leq\\ C ||f||_{L^1}^n. \\end{equation*}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2020 00:53:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-09"}
