metric study to predict the influence of elastic anisotropy on the\nnucleation and propagation of fracture in the brittle regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2020 02:07:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-12"}
