ted from our swarm robotic boats integrating\nthe adaptive latching system and performing the towing and guiding use cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2020 00:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2020 05:14:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-04"}
